                    <span>I have not yet read this book.  It looks exciting and I hope I enjoy it.  I am reading this book for a report in JROTC.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">GREAT READING FOR BLACK WOMEN</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>4</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
